# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Allowlist model: nothing is tracked unless it is explicitly re-included
# below. Stray files stay out of the repo by default (a NOTES.md or plan.md
# dropped at the root, a .claude/ working directory, a one-off doc under docs/,
# a build binary, local Terraform state) instead of relying on us to anticipate
# and block each one. To start tracking a genuinely new path, add a "!" line.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# 1. Root: ignore every entry, and any dot-directory at any depth (a nested
#    .claude/, .terraform/, and the like), then re-include the known ones. The
#    dot-directory rule precedes the re-includes, so !/.github/ still wins.
/*
.*/
!/.github/
!/.gitignore
!/.goreleaser.yml
!/assets/
!/CHANGELOG.md
!/cmd/
!/docs/
!/examples/
!/GNUmakefile
!/go.mod
!/go.sum
!/internal/
!/LICENSE
!/main.go
!/README.md
!/templates/
!/terraform-registry-manifest.json
!/tools/

# 2. docs/ is generated by `go generate ./...`; only the generated shapes
#    belong. A hand-added file or directory under docs/ (for example a
#    docs/superpowers/ spec) is ignored.
/docs/*
!/docs/functions/
!/docs/index.md

# 3. templates/: only the hand-authored index template is tracked. The
#    per-function templates are regenerated by cmd/gendoctemplates from each
#    package's Functions() registry, and are not committed.
/templates/*
!/templates/index.md.tmpl
/templates/functions/

# 4. Within each included source directory, track only the file types that
#    belong there; anything else is ignored without being named. The "!.../**/"
#    line in each block re-includes subdirectories so git descends into them.
/internal/**
!/internal/**/
!/internal/**/*.go
!/internal/**/*.bin
!/internal/**/*.txt
!/internal/**/*.md

/cmd/**
!/cmd/**/
!/cmd/**/*.go

/tools/**
!/tools/**/
!/tools/**/*.go

/examples/**
!/examples/**/
!/examples/**/*.tf

/assets/**
!/assets/**/
!/assets/**/*.svg

/.github/**
!/.github/**/
!/.github/**/*.yml
!/.github/**/*.yaml
!/.github/**/*.md
